description:
This unique place has a style all its own.

Palazio Serviced Apartment Taman Mount Austin

New renovation ( May 2024)
Stylish muji studio
17th floor with city view

Free WiFi with high speed broadband
1 free dedicated indoor car parking lot ( for car only)
Motorbike can park at unsheltered visitor carpark with rm20 per night per motor*


Self-check-in
Digital door lock
24 hours gate and guarded

The space
New renovation ( May 2024)
Stylish muji studio
17th floor with city view
Private bathroom
Kitchenette

Free WiFi with high speed broadband

Sleeping arrangement:
1 Queen bed with fresh bedsheet
1 Queen blanket
4 pillows
2 Fresh towels

In the unit, we have

1 Aircond
1 ceiling fan
Kitchenette
Microwave
Refrigerator
Electric Kettle
Dinning table
55 inches Smart TV
- Youtube and Netflix pre-installed ( need to sign in with own Netflix account)
- Washer dryer combo ( 2 in 1)
- 2 dental kits

Bathroom:
- Water heater
- Bidet spray
- sink
- mirror
- shampoo
- shower gel
- toilet papers

Guest access
Apartment Facilities :

1) Ground floor,
~ Small swimming pool for adult
~ Gymnasium
~ Playground

2) Level 5 :
~ Swimming pools ( Adult pool and Kids pool )
~ Gymnasium
~ Playground

Other things to note
Check-in time : After 3pm
Checkout time : 11am

For early check-in and late checkout, the additional charge is ( MYR ) RM20 per extra hour.
Subject to the availability. Please check with us first. Thank you.

reviews.comments:
My husband and I stayed 3 nights here at Palazio. This is our 2nd booking with GDragon Homestay. We love how easy it is to check-in. And their team is prompt in replies and very clear in their instructions.
What we like about the apartment:
- The apartment is as shown in the images in the listing.
- Easy to order Grab Food because they could deliver up to apartment.
- The hairdryer provided is strong and good.
- The location is near Mount Austin, grab rides are all within RM5-7 to nearby Aeon Tebrau, Toppen, Mount Austin.
- Washing machine is clean to use.
- They provide a rack with hangers for us to dry our clothes.
- Broom, scissor, cutlery all available which is definitely great.
What we didn't like about the apartment:
- The unit faces the lift lobby so it can get noisy for light sleepers.
- There is some slight renovation going on at nearby units so it was quite noisy for us when we wanted to rest/nap in the afternoon.
- low water pressure from the showerhead.
- The mattress is
Superior interior design. Love it so much! Feel so comfortable staying!

The check in process was easy and fuss free. Clear instructions were given and all questions were answered almost immediately. Place is clean and all amenities worked well. Thank you for being such gracious hosts!
Clean envrionment and host was very responsive and helpful in giving clear instructions for stay. Worth the bucks üôè

userProfile.about:
We love traveling and we found many people like to rent a place which feel like a home, we decided to start running homestay in JB area. 
We also manage homestay for other owners. 
Currently, GDRAGON homestay can be found in Palazio Mount Austin, Mosaic Southkey, KSL D'Esplanade, Parc Regency Plentong, Encorp Marina Puteri Harbour, Pinetree, Royal Strand Danga Bay, Lovell, Bay point, Paradigm Residence and Central Park.
